        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>You fill the creature's mind with a terrifying vision out of its nightmares. The target must attempt a Will save. If the target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Unconscious]{Unconscious} when you Cast this Spell on it, it immediately wakes up before attempting its save, and if it fails its save, it gains the @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Fleeing]{Fleeing} condition for 1 round in addition to the effects noted above.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 3}.</p>"
